// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0650 — Mass File Rename (anubis)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9904ede9-d4aa-512d-880a-943262113692

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
